Huawei is running a Spring Special in September with massive discounts on their latest smartphones, fitness bands and smart watches. Deals included in the sale are the Huawei P30 Pro with complimentary FreeLace and 7,000mAh for only R15,999, as well as the Huawei P20 Pro for only R9,499 – saving you R4,500. Many of the sale items also come with an additional gift. Deals are available online, and are valid until stocks last. T’s and C’s apply. Deals in Huawei’s Spring Sale are listed below. For more information or to view the deals, visit the Huawei website. Available in two colour options. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-319289" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e-400x400.jpg 400w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e-430x430.jpg 430w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-319291" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e_.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e_.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e_-400x400.jpg 400w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e_-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Band-3e_-430x430.jpg 430w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-319293" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/P20-PRO.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp